019package com.plotsquared.core.plot.flag;
020
021/**
022 * These are flags used in PlotSquared and PlotSquared
023 * add-ons that can be used to associate information
024 * with the plot, without users being able to access the
025 * information.
026 * <p>
027 * These flags are not user assignable, nor do they
028 * show up in `/plot info`, `/plot flag list`, etc.
029 * <p>
030 * PlotSquared add-ons should ignore these flags
031 * when outputting flag information to users. An example
032 * of such a scenario would be the flag listing in Dynmap.
033 */
034public interface InternalFlag {
035
036}
